thread.title: Patryk Mania

author: Patryk Mania
title: Patryk Mania
text: Nice and clean user portal. All information are there. Can't tell if they are good with dealing with accidents because I never had one with them. But if you are looking for the cheapest of the cheapest insurance you can untick all the boxes during the insurance setup and end up with the insurance that is half of the cost. Of course then you will have more trouble if any accident will happen. I personally chose the highest option possible, still paying <900e for <30y old for 1.4l and not even a full no claim bonus.
